reviewText: Everything on this goes way too fast, but for some reason me great tips are left out - that can be found several places online. Basic bows are covered but nothing really great.
This dvd was what a friend wanted, she is pleased with it except it does not play in all dvd players....

the video is pretty good. this video has some good tips, but does go too fast.  I know I can pause it, and I do...but it would be better if it were a bit slower.  for some reason it only plays on some of our dvd players, I know it is this video b/c we have tried others and they have worked fine.
